                                <dt id="endnote_en_77"><a class="pdec_endnote" href="#endnote_en_77_ref">77t</a></dt><dd>
                                    Cave, Ashton, and Mitford translate this as a “Malacca cane.”</dd>
                                <dt id="endnote_en_78"><a class="pdec_endnote" href="#endnote_en_78_ref">78t</a></dt><dd> This
                                    rendering, which may be controversial, continues with the notion that “faveur” in love
