                                <dt id="endnote_en_80"><a class="pdec_endnote" href="#endnote_en_80_ref">80t</a></dt><dd>
                                    “Charming” (Cave and Perry-Lyons); “adorable” (Buss); “lovable” (Ashton”).</dd>
                                <dt id="endnote_en_81"><a class="pdec_endnote" href="#endnote_en_81_ref">81t</a></dt><dd> To
                                    capture this “horreur”: “I dread living” (Perry-Lyons), “Life would be repugnant to me”
